WEBVTT

00:01.167 --> 00:02.725
<i>NARRATOR: Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.802 --> 00:05.737
- I still love you, Lucas.
- Peyton, I...

00:08.375 --> 00:11.503
<i>(WON'TLET YOU GO</i> PLAYING)

00:11.978 --> 00:14.105
Lucas asked me to marry him.

00:16.349 --> 00:18.044
MAN: What the hell is this?

00:18.118 --> 00:20.985
- Well, we have this website.
- Yeah, we're sports announcers.

00:21.054 --> 00:23.079
(ALL CHEERING)

00:23.156 --> 00:24.748
Everyone get away from the door!

00:24.824 --> 00:27.691
- Jim, you can't do this.
- It's a little late for that, Mouth.

00:28.395 --> 00:30.363
You're bleeding.
We gotta get you somewhere safe.

00:30.430 --> 00:33.797
- Come on.
- No, I can't. I can't walk. I tried.

00:33.933 --> 00:35.332
Jimmy, please.

00:35.402 --> 00:37.836
- I'm sorry.
- No!

00:37.904 --> 00:39.269
(GUN FIRING)

00:39.339 --> 00:40.966
He was my friend.

00:42.942 --> 00:45.911
I... I miss him a lot.

00:53.153 --> 00:55.144
Lucas, look me in the eye

00:55.221 --> 00:56.779
and tell me that that kiss did not feel

00:56.856 --> 00:59.586
exactly the same as it felt three years ago.

01:01.961 --> 01:04.156
I'm in love with her, Peyton.

